dcterms:creator: Fraxtil
dcterms:description: A dataset containing 90 songs choreographed by a single author named Fraxtil, with five charts per song corresponding to increasing difficulty levels.
dcterms:title: Fraxtil

dcterms:description: A larger, multi-author collection called In The Groove (ITG) containing 133 songs with one chart per difficulty, except for 13 songs that lack charts for the highest difficulty.
dcterms:title: In The Groove (ITG)
